#Reverso
_ 
Reverso Tribute Minute Repeater 
Designed, made and assembled in our Manufacture

A distinctive signature.
#Reverso 
_
Reverso One 
Designed, made and assembled in our Manufacture
_
Characterised by the three emblematic gadroons, the Reverso One keeps its inspiration from the Art Deco design. The rectangular case associated with the bold colour of its dial, displays a singular look with an irresistible touch of modernity. 
_

node.text:
A bold and feminine style. 
#Reverso
_
Reverso One
Designed, made and assembled in our Manufacture
_
Feminine, graceful, and timeless, the Reverso One draws inspiration from the original Reverso ladies’ watch. With its matching alligator strap, this feminine timepiece adorns the wrist in an original and bold colour, a burgundy red as deep as it is bewitching. 
_
#JaegerLeCoultre #Reverso #HomeofFineWatchmaking #SwissWatch #ValleeDeJoux #Watchmaking #Craftsmanship #SavoirFaire
